explains: v. 重叠；与……重合（overlap 的现在分词）
wordGroup: overlap ratio 纵向重合度；重叠比
overlap joint 搭接接头；重迭结合
overlap region 重叠区；重叠区域

sentences.en: The now-famous cantilever hovers over an urban plaza consisting of overlapping zones.
sentences.cn: 现在著名的悬臂悬挑在城市广场上，广场由重叠的区域组成。

sentences.en: The floor was protected with overlapping sheets of newspaper.
sentences.cn: 地板用一张搭着一张的报纸保护着。
